(v1 is (Vector of W1) & v2 is (Vector of W2)) by A10,A11,STRUCT_0:def 5;
then reconsider w1 = v1,w2 = v2 as (Vector of ( W1 + W2 )) by A4,A2,VECTSP_4:10;
A13: ( v1 + v2 ) = ( w1 + w2 ) by VECTSP_4:13;
v2 in (the carrier of ( Lin B29 )) by A5,A11,STRUCT_0:def 5;
